data.description: Welcome Home to 636 Hartwell Rd – Lavonia’s Farmhouse in the City!  This home is situated stately on a serene corner lot, exuding traditional farmhouse charm throughout yet at every turn of this almost 1900 sqft home there is unspeakable creative character. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, all generously sized, this recently renovated abode offers a perfect blend of rustic elegance and modern convenience. Step inside to discover a haven of comfort and style, where shiplap and tongue & groove accent walls seamlessly blend with wood trim beams, creating an inviting atmosphere all around you. The heart of the home is the chef's kitchen, featuring gleaming granite countertops, modern appliances, and a captivating tile backsplash. An alcove dining room sets the stage for memorable meals, an inviting living room for all your social gatherings, while a separate laundry room and pantry provide needed added convenience. Relax and unwind on the inviting front porch, or retreat to the fenced-in yard, complete with a charming pergola and play area providing the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings or simply relaxing under the sun. You can easily take a stroll to downtown Lavonia through your sidewalk gate in this desirable neighborhood, residents of 636 Hartwell Rd enjoy easy access to downtown shopping, dining, schools, parks and community events. Plus, with easy access to Interstate and Highways, commuting to nearby cities will be a breeze. The stacked river stone foundation adds to the attraction of this captivating property, while the striking grey exterior with eye-catching white trim ensures curb appeal that stands out. This home is not just a place to live; it's a lifestyle. Experience the tranquility of country living with all the amenities of modern life. Don't miss your chance to make 636 Hartwell Rd your own slice of paradise in Lavonia. Schedule a showing today and prepare to fall in love!
